content.rendered:
Directed by Anil Ravipudi

Written by Anil Ravipudi. G. Adi Narayana

Star Tamannaah Bhatia (Harika). Pooja Hegde. Venkatesh Daggubati (Venky). Mehreen Pirzada (Honey). Varun Tej (Varun). Sunil ((as Suneel)). Rajendra Prasad (Prasad). Pragathi. Raghu Babu (Anji Reddy). Imam Hossain Saju (Playback Singer). Annapoorna. Vijaya Y. Pradeep

Language Telugu

Producers S. Krishna. Dil Raju. B. Sridhar Rao. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations
